14 TL
(bash) Tj T*
(git init) Tj T*
(git add .) Tj T*
(git commit -m "Initial OpenClaw crypto wallet intelligence starter package") Tj T*
(git branch -M main) Tj T*
(git remote add origin YOUR_GITHUB_REPOSITORY_URL) Tj T*
(git push -u origin main) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Do not commit real secrets or real .env files.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. GIVE OPENCLAW THE PROJECT MEMORY) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(In OpenClaw, add the files from /memory as project memory/context:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Project Memory.md) Tj T*
(- Agent Operating Rules.md) Tj T*
(- Security Memory.md) Tj T*
(- Product Vision.md) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(These files tell OpenClaw what the system is, how it should behave, what must not be) Tj T*
(built, and how to prioritise work.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. GIVE OPENCLAW THE INITIAL KICKOFF PROMPT) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Open:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(docs/openclaw-prompts/00_Initial_Kickoff_Prompt.md) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Paste it into OpenClaw and instruct it to begin Stage 0 only.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Do not ask OpenClaw to build the entire system in one pass.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. ADD ANTHROPIC FALLBACK EARLY) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Open:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(docs/openclaw-prompts/03_Anthropic_Fallback_Setup_Prompt.md) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use this prompt after the project repo exists and before heavy development begins.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Development routing should be:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Ollama qwen3:4b for low-risk cleanup and classification.) Tj T*
(2. ChatGPT as the primary development model.) Tj T*
(3. Anthropic as fallback if ChatGPT token limits are reached.) Tj T*
(4. Latest suitable paid models only when the final system is used for higher-risk) Tj T*
(analysis.) Tj T*
ET
endstream
