() Tj T*
(6. INSTALL OLLAMA AND QWEN3:4B EARLY) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Open:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(docs/openclaw-prompts/02_Ollama_Setup_Prompt.md) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The only local model to install is:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(ollama pull qwen3:4b) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OpenClaw should confirm the model responds before continuing with research or scraping) Tj T*
(features.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(7. INSTALL POSTGRESQL) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Open:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(docs/openclaw-prompts/04_PostgreSQL_Setup_Prompt.md) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OpenClaw should help configure PostgreSQL locally using either Docker Compose or a) Tj T*
(native install. The included Docker Compose file binds PostgreSQL to localhost only.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(8. FOLLOW THE STAGED PLAN) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OpenClaw must work stage by stage:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Stage 0 - Foundation, repository, security and local infrastructure) Tj T*
(2. Stage 1 - Wallet database and movement tracking) Tj T*
(3. Stage 2 - Price outcomes and signal validation) Tj T*
(4. Stage 3 - Core pattern intelligence) Tj T*
(5. Stage 4 - Controlled research) Tj T*
(6. Stage 5 - Copy-trade candidates and paper trading) Tj T*
(7. Stage 6 - Reporting and feedback optimisation) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(V1 is not complete until Stage 6 is complete and ASVS score is at least 90%.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(IMPORTANT SAFETY RULES) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(V1 must not execute real trades.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The system must not:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Store wallet private keys) Tj T*
(- Ask for seed phrases) Tj T*
(- Store exchange withdrawal keys) Tj T*
ET
endstream
