() Tj T*
(BACKUP AND MIGRATION) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Backup and restore must be implemented early.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The goal is to make it easy to move this system later to a more powerful computer by:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Cloning the GitHub repository.) Tj T*
(2. Installing dependencies.) Tj T*
(3. Pulling Ollama qwen3:4b.) Tj T*
(4. Restoring the PostgreSQL backup.) Tj T*
(5. Configuring .env.) Tj T*
(6. Running migrations.) Tj T*
(7. Starting backend, frontend and workers.) Tj T*
(8. Running validation checks.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use the prompts and scripts in this package to maintain that migration path from the) Tj T*
(beginning.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(RECOMMENDED FIRST OPENCLAW INSTRUCTION) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Paste this into OpenClaw after loading the memory files:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(text) Tj T*
(Use the repository files and project memory provided. Begin Stage 0 only. Do not build) Tj T*
(application features yet. Create the repository structure, configure documentation, set) Tj T*
(up PostgreSQL, install and test Ollama qwen3:4b, add Anthropic fallback model routing,) Tj T*
(create the initial FastAPI and React skeletons, create the ASVS audit register) Tj T*
(foundation, and update the README. Stop after Stage 0 validation and provide a summary) Tj T*
ET
